The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited Key Developments

Geopolitical Risk Expert Presents at HSBC 5th Annual Asia Investor Forum – London, Jun-08-2017
Jun 6 17
Geopolitical Risk Expert Presents at HSBC 5th Annual Asia Investor Forum – London, Jun-08-2017 . Venue: The May Fair Hotel, Stratton Street, Mayfair, London, W1J 8LT, United Kingdom.


The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited Reports Consolidated Earnings Results for the Year Ended December 31, 2016
Mar 2 17
The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited reported consolidated earnings results for the year ended December 31, 2016. For the year, the company reported net interest income of HKD 96,908 million compared to HKD 94,377 million a year ago. Total operating income was HKD 232,738 million compared to HKD 235,945 million a year ago. Net operating income was HKD 162,598 million compared to HKD 178,440 million a year ago. Operating profit was HKD 87,795 million compared to HKD 101,449 million a year ago. Profit before tax was HKD 102,707 million compared to HKD 117,279 million a year ago. Profit for the period was HKD 84,795 million compared to HKD 99,983 million a year ago. Profit attributable to shareholders of the parent company was HKD 78,646 million compared to HKD 89,533 million a year ago.


The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited Presents at Digital Financial Services Indonesia Summit, Nov-08-2016
Oct 21 16
The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited Presents at Digital Financial Services Indonesia Summit, Nov-08-2016 . Venue: Shangri-La Hotel, Jakarta, Indonesia.


